4️⃣ ANALYTICS → BY TEMPLATE
Purpose: Structural quality evaluation.
Load from:
templateAnalytics/{templateId}

🟡 L1
Show:
    • Number of Runs
    • Avg Raw %
    • Avg Accuracy %
    • Raw % variance
    • Run comparison chart

🔵 L2
Add:
    • Stability Index per run
    • Phase adherence variance
    • Risk shift per run
    • Discipline stress score
    • Template Effectiveness Rating
Effectiveness Rating formula:
(Avg Raw % × 0.4) +
(Avg Discipline Index × 0.3) +
(1 - Risk Variance) × 0.3
Precomputed.

